!----------------------------------------------------------------------------!
! PLOT_HIST                                                                  !
! =========                                                                  !
!                                                                            !
! Neil Drummond, 8.2005                                                      !
!                                                                            !
! This utility reads in vmc.hist, vmc.hist2, dmc.hist and dmc.hist2 files    !
! and allows the user to plot his or her choice of data against move number. !
! The resulting vmc_data.plot and dmc_data.plot files can be read by         !
! XMGrace.  Several items of data may be plotted.                            !
!----------------------------------------------------------------------------!

